; This plugin determines the categories and their articles for the encyclopedia.
; Categories are listed in "encyclopedia" and their articles in sections of the same names.

; Flags can be used to enable/disable articles depending on game mode, or unlock them by default.
; In the case of unlocking, not having the flag will have the same effect as setting it to "0".

; A presence of a game mode flag means that its value will become a requirement, either "1" or "0".
; Should such a flag not exist, then no game mode will be required to enable/disable the article.
; Available game mode flags are: "azazel", "hardcore", "story" and "survival".

